Author: mithro_
Content: @everyone - https://platform.wafer.space is going down for ~1 hour (but hopefully less) while I upgrade it to the latest code. I'll restart any currently running checks after the update.

Author: mithro_
Content: https://platform.wafer.space/ is now up and running again with a shiny new coat of paint and some ultrafast precheck runners that have very high single thread performance and can handle a total of 14 concurrent tasks at once.

Author: mithro_
Content: You'll also have manufacturing check history now and the ability to download the output of precheck

Author: mithro_
Content: There is also some project metadata you can now set like license, if the project is public and a repo url.
